content: My three year old loves it

This is an absolutely wonderful game. There is so much attention to detail on this. I feel like maybe they should make a monkey preschool classroom for this one just because some of the things, like the paw prints for example, can be difficult to see why they would be for one animal vs. Another. Like have the play button for the games, but have a book button where you can touch each animal and have it show and tell a few little things about the animal. But again, I still think this is a 5 star game.
